text.tspan: has no knowledge but infinite intelligence.
Do not take over the keyboard!
This can be off-putting and scary.
Take it slow, it's about learning.
Let students try answering a question first.
Help with open questions. Encourage a discussion.
It's okay to make mistakes - that's where you learn
Be supportive, but let your student explore.
Use pen and paper or go to a whiteboard!
Drawing and visualising is really helpful.
